---
title: Beef Sizzle Stir-Fry with Bok Choy over Jasmine Rice
description: Stir-fries are a handy dish for weeknights because you can get them on the table quickly with minimal fuss. Just prep your protein and veg, whip together a simple sauce, and let those ingredients sizzle in the pan. For this version, we’re tossing beef strips, bell pepper, and bok choy in a marinade of ginger, garlic, and soy sauce. It’s simple yet tremendously satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-sizzle-stir-fry-1ea7ae54.jpg
